    public class SecondPassVisitor
extends at.tugraz.ist.soma.antlr.gen.JavaBaseVisitor<java.lang.String>
    This class adds information (line number, last line etc.) to a given Statement. This is done by using the auto generated visitor methods from the ANTLR-framework.
